N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 167.10 - Occupational skills program

State Regulations

Agencies proposing to offer an occupational skills program
or an occupational and basic skills program with funding from SECGP shall
comply with the provisions of sections
126.1, 126.2, 126.4, 126.5, 126.6, 126.8, 126.9
and
126.11
of this
